          <msContents>
            <summary>Text of praise to appease the planet Saturn, performed to avert the misfortune, especially for kings, thought to be generated by its celestial movements; presented as a discourse (saṃvāda) between the Hindu deities Śiva and Umā.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
